  "title": "Isolation of Putative Disease Resistance Gene Clones from Chickpea and Pigeonpea",
  "abstract": "Nucleotide binding sites conferring disease resistance were cloned from chickpea (Cicer arietinum) and pigeon pea (Cajanus cajan). The majority of amplified resistance gene candidates showed high homology to N (tobacco) and L6 (flax) resistance genes.",
